snippet.title: Naheulbeuk's Dungeon Master - Game Reveal Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description:
Build a lair and manage your minions in Naheulbeuk's Dungeon Master, revealed today at the PC Gaming Show 2023. Defend your dungeon from adventurers who want to fill their pockets with loot while keeping your underlings happy enough to avoid HR problems. Read more at PC Gamer: https://www.pcgamer.com/naheulbeuks-dungeon-master-reveal-trailer-pcgs-2023
